WITH "cte" ("player_id") AS (SELECT "wimbledon" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "us_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "au_open" FROM "championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" NATURAL CROSS JOIN "players" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name"

SELECT * FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "Wimbledon"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "Fr_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "US_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "Au_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "p") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "c" GROUP BY 1,2) AS "tmp" WHERE "grand_slams_count"!=0

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM("grand_slams_count") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ((SELECT "c"."wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" RIGHT JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "c"."wimbledon"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "c"."wimbledon") UNION ALL (SELECT "c"."Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" RIGHT JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "c"."Fr_open") UNION ALL (SELECT "c"."US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" RIGHT JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "c"."US_open"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "c"."US_open") UNION ALL (SELECT "a"."Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" RIGHT JOIN "championships" AS "a" ON "a"."Au_open"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "a"."Au_open")) AS "t" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON "p"."player_id"="t"."player_id" GROUP BY "t"."player_id"

WITH "w" AS (SELECT "year","Wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "Championships"), "f" AS (SELECT "year","Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships"), "u" AS (SELECT "year","US_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships"), "a" AS (SELECT "year","Au_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT("c"."id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT * FROM "w" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "f" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "u" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "a") AS "c" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "c"."id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "p"."player_name" ORDER BY "p"."player_name"

SELECT "player_id","player_name","grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="Wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="Fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="US_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="Au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" CROSS JOIN "Championships" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name") AS "tb1" WHERE "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM("grand_slams_count") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "p") CROSS JOIN (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT("Wimbledon") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Fr_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("US_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") AS "t" WHERE "p"."player_id"="t"."player_id" GROUP BY "p"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("Wimbledon"="player_id")+SUM("Fr_open"="player_id")+SUM("US_open"="player_id")+SUM("AU_open"="player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" JOIN "Championships" ON "player_id"="Wimbledon" OR "player_id"="Fr_open" OR "player_id"="US_open" OR "player_id"="Au_open" GROUP BY "player_id"

SELECT "P"."player_id","P"."player_name",COUNT("P"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") AS "Champ" JOIN "Players" AS "P" ON "Champ"."player_id"="P"."player_id" GROUP BY "P"."player_id","P"."player_name"

SELECT "T"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM("cnt") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") AS "T" CROSS, "Players" AS "p" WHERE "T"."player_id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("player_id"="Wimbledon")+SUM("player_id"="fr_open")+SUM("player_id"="US_open")+SUM("player_id"="au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" LEFT JOIN "Players" ON "player_id" IN ("wimbledon","fr_open","us_open","au_open") GROUP BY 2,1

WITH "champs" AS (SELECT "year","wimbledon" AS "chm","b"."player_name",1 AS "slams" FROM "championships" AS "a" JOIN "players" AS "b" ON "a"."wimbledon"="b"."player_id" UNION ALL SELECT "year","fr_open" AS "chm","b"."player_name",1 AS "slams" FROM "championships" AS "a" JOIN "players" AS "b" ON "a"."fr_open"="b"."player_id" UNION ALL SELECT "year","us_open" AS "chm","b"."player_name",1 AS "slams" FROM "championships" AS "a" JOIN "players" AS "b" ON "a"."us_open"="b"."player_id" UNION ALL SELECT "year","au_open" AS "chm","b"."player_name",1 AS "slams" FROM "championships" AS "a" JOIN "players" AS "b" ON "a"."au_open"="b"."player_id") SELECT "chm" AS "player_id","player_name",SUM("slams") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "champs" GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",COALESCE(SUM("c"."Wimbledon"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."US_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."Au_open"="p"."player_id"), 0) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Championships" AS "c") CROSS JOIN "players" AS "p" GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "a"."player_id","a"."player_name",COUNT("b"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "a") CROSS JOIN (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") AS "b" WHERE "a"."player_id"="b"."player_id" GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 3 DESC

SELECT "tmp"."player_id","player_name",SUM("num") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "num" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "num" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "num" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "num" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") AS "tmp" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "tmp"."player_id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT "t1"."player_id","t1"."player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="t2"."wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="t2"."fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="t2"."us_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="t2"."au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "t1" JOIN "championships" AS "t2" ON "t2"."wimbledon"="t1"."player_id" OR "t2"."fr_open"="t1"."player_id" OR "t2"."us_open"="t1"."player_id" OR "t2"."au_open"="t1"."player_id" GROUP BY "t1"."player_id"

WITH "base" AS (SELECT "year",'Wimbledon' AS "game","Wimbledon" AS "winner" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Fr_open' AS "game","Fr_open" AS "winner" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'US_open' AS "game","US_open" AS "winner" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Au_open' AS "game","Au_open" AS "winner" FROM "Championships"), "base2" AS (SELECT "winner",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "base" GROUP BY 1) SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","b"."grand_slams_count" FROM "base2" AS "b" JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "b"."winner"="p"."player_id"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "year","wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","us_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships") SELECT "cte"."player_id","player_name",COUNT("year") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" JOIN "players" AS "p" USING ("player_id") GROUP BY 1,2

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "one_gs_count",'Wimbledon' AS "grand_slam" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "one_gs_count",'Fr_open' AS "grand_slam" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "one_gs_count",'US_open' AS "grand_slam" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "one_gs_count",'Au_open' AS "grand_slam" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") SELECT "t"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM("one_gs_count") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "temp" AS "t" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "t"."player_id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "player_id"

SELECT "a"."player_id","a"."player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."Wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."Fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."US_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."Au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" AS "a" LEFT JOIN "Championships" AS "b" ON "a"."player_id"="b"."Wimbledon" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."Fr_open" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."US_open" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."Au_open" GROUP BY "a"."player_id" HAVING "grand_slams_count"!=0

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player_id") AS "num_tournament" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."wimbledon" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player_id") AS "num_tournament" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."fr_open" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player_id") AS "num_tournament" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."us_open" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player_id") AS "num_tournament" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."au_open" GROUP BY 1,2) SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("num_tournament") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "temp" GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY "grand_slams_count"

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "year",'Wimbledon' AS "col","Wimbledon" AS "value" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Fr_open' AS "col","Fr_open" AS "value" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'US_open' AS "col","US_open" AS "value" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Au_open' AS "col","Au_open" AS "value" FROM "Championships") SELECT "temp"."value" AS "player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT("temp"."value") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "temp" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON "temp"."value"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "temp"."value" ORDER BY "player_id"

SELECT "tb2"."winner" AS "player_id","p"."player_name","tb2"."num" AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "winner",COUNT("winner") AS "num" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "winner" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" FROM "Championships") AS "tb" GROUP BY 1) AS "tb2" JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "tb2"."winner"="p"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("player_id"="wimbledon")+SUM("player_id"="fr_open")+SUM("player_id"="us_open")+SUM("player_id"="au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" JOIN "championships" ON "player_id"="wimbledon" OR "player_id"="fr_open" OR "player_id"="us_open" OR "player_id"="au_open" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name" ORDER BY 3 DESC

SELECT "A"."c" AS "player_id","P"."player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "c" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "c" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "c" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "c" FROM "Championships") AS "A" JOIN "Players" AS "P" ON "A"."c"="P"."player_id" GROUP BY "A"."c","P"."player_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "cte"."player_id","players"."player_name",COUNT("cte"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" LEFT JOIN "Players" ON "cte"."player_id"="players"."player_id" GROUP BY "cte"."player_id","players"."player_name" ORDER BY "player_id" DESC

WITH "win" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "player_id","year" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id","year" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id","year" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "AU_open" AS "player_id","year" FROM "championships" ORDER BY "player_id","year") SELECT "a"."player_id","b"."player_name",COUNT("a"."year") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "win" AS "a" LEFT JOIN "players" AS "b" ON "a"."player_id"="b"."player_id" GROUP BY "a"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("c"."wimbledon"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."fr_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."us_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."au_open"="p"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("championships" AS "c") CROSS JOIN "players" AS "p" GROUP BY 1 HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "b"."player_id","p"."player_name","b"."grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "prize" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "prize" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "prize" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "prize" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "prize" FROM "Championships") AS "a" GROUP BY "prize") AS "b" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "b"."player_id"="p"."player_id"

WITH "t1" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT("Wimbledon") AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Fr_open") AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("US_open") AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Au_open") AS "cnt" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") SELECT "t1"."player_id","player_name",SUM("cnt") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "t1" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON ("t1"."player_id"="p"."player_id") GROUP BY "t1"."player_id"

SELECT * FROM (SELECT "player_id","player_name",(SELECT COUNT(CASE WHEN "Wimbledon"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)+COUNT(CASE WHEN "Fr_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)+COUNT(CASE WHEN "US_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)+COUNT(CASE WHEN "Au_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) FROM "Championships") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players") AS "A" WHERE "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("year") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","year" FROM "Players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" AS "w" ON "p"."player_id"="w"."Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","year" FROM "Players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" AS "f" ON "p"."player_id"="f"."Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","year" FROM "Players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" AS "u" ON "p"."player_id"="u"."US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","year" FROM "Players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" AS "a" ON "p"."player_id"="a"."Au_open") AS "t" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name"

WITH "tournaments" AS (SELECT "year",'wimbledon' AS "tournament","wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Fr_open' AS "tournament","Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'US_open' AS "tournament","US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Au_open' AS "tournament","Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships") SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT("year") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "tournaments" AS "t" ON "p"."player_id"="t"."player_id" GROUP BY "p"."player_id"

WITH "CTE" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" JOIN "CTE" ON "Players"."player_id"="CTE"."id" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name"

SELECT "a".*,SUM(CASE WHEN "player_id"="Wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="Fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="US_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "player_id"="Au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "a") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "b" GROUP BY 1 HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "T1"."player_id","player_name",SUM("wins") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" AS "T1" JOIN (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT("Wimbledon") AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Fr_open") AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("US_open") AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT("Au_open") AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") AS "T2" ON ("T1"."player_id"="T2"."player_id") GROUP BY "player_id" ORDER BY "player_id" DESC

SELECT "a"."player_id","a"."player_name",SUM("a"."w") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",((CASE WHEN "c"."Wimbledon"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+(CASE WHEN "c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+(CASE WHEN "c"."US_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+(CASE WHEN "c"."Au_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS "w" FROM "Players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Wimbledon" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."Fr_open" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."US_open" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."Au_open") AS "a" GROUP BY "a"."player_id","a"."player_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "us_open" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "au_open" AS "id" FROM "championships") SELECT "c"."id" AS "player_id","player_name",COUNT("id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" AS "c" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON "c"."id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "id"

WITH "t" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" LEFT JOIN "t" USING ("player_id") WHERE "t"."player_id" IS NOT NULL GROUP BY "player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Wimbledon"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Fr_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."US_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Au_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "b" GROUP BY "player_id" HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

WITH "w" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "amount" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1), "f" AS (SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "amount" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1), "u" AS (SELECT "US_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "amount" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1), "a" AS (SELECT "Au_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "amount" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1), "all1" AS (SELECT * FROM "w" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "f" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "u" UNION ALL SELECT * FROM "a") SELECT "id" AS "player_id","Players"."player_name",SUM("amount") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "all1" LEFT JOIN "Players" ON "all1"."id"="Players"."Player_id" GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "c"."Wimbledon"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "c"."US_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN "c"."Au_open"="p"."player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "p") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "c" GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

WITH "win_occ" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "Players"."player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" JOIN "win_occ" ON "Players"."player_id"="win_occ"."player_id" GROUP BY 1

SELECT "B"."player" AS "player_id","P"."player_name","B"."grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "A"."player",COUNT("A"."player") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships") AS "A" GROUP BY "A"."player") AS "B" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "P" ON "B"."player"="P"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("p"."player_id"="c"."Wimbledon")+SUM("p"."player_id"="c"."Fr_open")+SUM("p"."player_id"="c"."US_open")+SUM("p"."player_id"="c"."Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "p") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "c" GROUP BY 1 HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT * FROM (SELECT "ans"."player_id","ans"."player_name",("Wimbledon"+"fr_open"+"US_open"+"Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "w1"."player_id","w1"."player_name","w1"."Wimbledon","f1"."fr_open","u1"."US_open","a1"."Au_open" FROM (((SELECT "w"."player_id","w"."player_name",COUNT("w"."Wimbledon") AS "Wimbledon" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","c"."year" AS "Wimbledon" FROM "Players" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Wimbledon") AS "w" GROUP BY "w"."player_id","w"."player_name") AS "w1" LEFT JOIN (SELECT "f"."player_id","f"."player_name",COUNT("f"."fr_open") AS "fr_open" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","c"."year" AS "fr_open" FROM "Players" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Fr_open") AS "f" GROUP BY "f"."player_id","f"."player_name") AS "f1" ON "w1"."player_id"="f1"."player_id" AND "w1"."player_name"="f1"."player_name") LEFT JOIN (SELECT "u"."player_id","u"."player_name",COUNT("u"."US_open") AS "US_open" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","c"."year" AS "US_open" FROM "Players" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."US_open") AS "u" GROUP BY "u"."player_id","u"."player_name") AS "u1" ON "w1"."player_id"="u1"."player_id" AND "w1"."player_name"="u1"."player_name") LEFT JOIN (SELECT "a"."player_id","a"."player_name",COUNT("a"."Au_open") AS "Au_open" FROM (SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","c"."year" AS "Au_open" FROM "Players" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Au_open") AS "a" GROUP BY "a"."player_id","a"."player_name") AS "a1" ON "w1"."player_id"="a1"."player_id" AND "w1"."player_name"="a1"."player_name") AS "ans") AS "ans1" WHERE "ans1"."grand_slams_count">0

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1), "cte2" AS (SELECT "player_id",SUM("wins") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" GROUP BY 1) SELECT "a"."player_id","player_name","grand_slams_count" FROM "cte2" AS "a" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "b" ON "a"."player_id"="b"."player_id"

SELECT "t"."player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" JOIN (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "fr_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "us_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "au_open" FROM "championships") AS "t" USING ("player_id") GROUP BY 1,2

WITH "total_wins_player" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "championships" GROUP BY "wimbledon" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "championships" GROUP BY "Fr_open" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "US_open" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "wins" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY "Au_open") SELECT "a"."player_id","player_name","a"."grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "player_id",SUM("wins") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "total_wins_player" GROUP BY "player_id") AS "a" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON "p"."player_id"="a"."player_id"

SELECT "P"."player_id","P"."player_name",(SUM("C"."Wimbledon"="P"."player_id")+SUM("C"."Fr_Open"="P"."player_id")+SUM("C"."US_Open"="P"."player_id")+SUM("C"."Au_Open"="P"."player_id")) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players" AS "P") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "C" GROUP BY "P"."player_id" HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM("c"."Wimbledon"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."US_open"="p"."player_id")+SUM("c"."Au_open"="p"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Championships" AS "c" JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "c"."Wimbledon"="p"."player_id" OR "c"."Fr_open"="p"."player_id" OR "c"."US_open"="p"."player_id" OR "c"."Au_open"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "p"."player_id","p"."player_name"

WITH "CTE1" AS (SELECT "WIMBLEDON" AS "GRAND_SLAM_WINNER" FROM "CHAMPIONSHIPS" UNION ALL SELECT "FR_OPEN" AS "GRAND_SLAM_WINNER" FROM "CHAMPIONSHIPS" UNION ALL SELECT "US_OPEN" AS "GRAND_SLAM_WINNER" FROM "CHAMPIONSHIPS" UNION ALL SELECT "AU_OPEN" AS "GRAND_SLAM_WINNER" FROM "CHAMPIONSHIPS") SELECT "PLAYER_ID","PLAYER_NAME",COUNT("GRAND_SLAM_WINNER") AS "GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT" FROM "PLAYERS" AS "P" JOIN "CTE1" ON "P"."PLAYER_ID"="CTE1"."GRAND_SLAM_WINNER" GROUP BY "PLAYER_ID","PLAYER_NAME"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "year","wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","us_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year","au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "championships") SELECT "players"."player_id","player_name",COUNT("cte"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" JOIN "cte" ON "players"."player_id"="cte"."player_id" GROUP BY "player_id"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "ids",COUNT("Wimbledon") AS "win" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open",COUNT("Fr_open") FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "US_open",COUNT("US_open") FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open",COUNT("Au_open") FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1) SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name","temp"."wn" AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN (SELECT "cte"."ids",SUM("win") AS "wn" FROM "cte" GROUP BY 1) AS "temp" ON "temp"."ids"="p"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("player_id"="Wimbledon")+SUM("player_id"="Fr_open")+SUM("player_id"="US_open")+SUM("player_id"="Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" JOIN "Championships" ON "player_id"="Wimbledon" OR "player_id"="Fr_open" OR "player_id"="US_open" OR "player_id"="Au_open" GROUP BY "player_id"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."wimbledon" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Fr_open" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."US_open" GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."Au_open" GROUP BY 1,2) SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("grand_slams_count") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" GROUP BY 1,2

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT("id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "p"."player_id"="cte"."id" GROUP BY 1

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" AS "P" JOIN "temp" ON "P"."player_id"="temp"."id" GROUP BY "player_id"

WITH "W1" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships"), "W2" AS (SELECT "player_id",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "W1" GROUP BY "player_id") SELECT "P"."player_id","P"."player_name","W2"."grand_slams_count" FROM "Players" AS "P" JOIN "W2" ON "P"."player_id"="W2"."player_id"

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "p"."player_id"="c"."wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "p"."player_id"="c"."fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "p"."player_id"="c"."us_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "p"."player_id"="c"."au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "championships" AS "c" ON "p"."player_id"="c"."wimbledon" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."fr_open" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."us_open" OR "p"."player_id"="c"."au_open" GROUP BY "p"."player_id","p"."player_name"

WITH "CTE" AS (SELECT "year",'Wimbledon' AS "match_name","Wimbledon" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Fr_open' AS "match_name","Fr_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'US_open' AS "match_name","US_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "year",'Au_open' AS "match_name","Au_open" AS "player" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("player") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "CTE" JOIN "players" AS "p" ON "cte"."player"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "player_id","player_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "cte" JOIN "Players" USING ("player_id") GROUP BY "player_id"

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") SELECT "temp"."player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "temp" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "temp"."player_id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "temp"."player_id"

SELECT "p"."player_id","p"."player_name",COUNT("p"."player_id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Us_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "player_id" FROM "Championships") AS "num_wins" JOIN "Players" AS "p" ON "num_wins"."player_id"="p"."player_id" GROUP BY "p"."player_id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT("year") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ((SELECT "player_id","player_name","year" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" WHERE "player_id"="Wimbledon") UNION ALL (SELECT "player_id","player_name","year" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" WHERE "player_id"="Fr_open") UNION ALL (SELECT "player_id","player_name","year" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" WHERE "player_id"="US_open") UNION ALL (SELECT "player_id","player_name","year" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" WHERE "player_id"="Au_open")) AS "T" GROUP BY "player_id"

SELECT "a"."player_id","a"."player_name",(SUM(CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."Wimbledon" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."fr_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."us_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "a"."player_id"="b"."au_open" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "a" JOIN "championships" AS "b" ON "a"."player_id"="b"."wimbledon" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."fr_open" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."us_open" OR "a"."player_id"="b"."au_open" GROUP BY "a"."player_id"

WITH "t1" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "player_id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "fr_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "us_open" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "au_open" FROM "championships") SELECT "t1"."player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "t1" JOIN "players" ON "t1"."player_id"="players"."player_id" GROUP BY 1

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Wimbledon"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Fr_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."US_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN "b"."Au_open"="player_id" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" AS "b" GROUP BY "player_id" HAVING "grand_slams_count">0

WITH "tmp" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "game" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "fr_open" AS "game" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "us_open" AS "game" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "au_open" AS "game" FROM "championships") SELECT "player_id","player_name",COUNT(1) AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" JOIN "tmp" ON "player_id"="game" GROUP BY 1,2

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT "wimbledon" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "id" FROM "championships" UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "id" FROM "championships") SELECT "temp"."id" AS "player_id","player_name",COUNT("temp"."id") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "temp" LEFT JOIN "players" ON "temp"."id"="players"."player_id" GROUP BY "temp"."id"

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("player_id"="Wimbledon")+SUM("player_id"="Fr_open")+SUM("player_id"="US_open")+SUM("player_id"="Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM ("Players") CROSS JOIN "Championships" GROUP BY "player_id" HAVING "grand_slams_count"!=0

SELECT "player_id","player_name",SUM("player_id"="Wimbledon")+SUM("player_id"="Fr_open")+SUM("player_id"="US_open")+SUM("player_id"="Au_open") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM "players" AS "p" JOIN "Championships" ON "player_id"="Wimbledon" OR "player_id"="Fr_open" OR "player_id"="US_open" OR "player_id"="Au_open" GROUP BY "player_id"

SELECT "a"."id" AS "player_id","b"."player_name",SUM("a"."title") AS "grand_slams_count" FROM (SELECT "Wimbledon" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "title" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Fr_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "title" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "US_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "title" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT "Au_open" AS "id",COUNT(1) AS "title" FROM "Championships" GROUP BY 1) AS "a" LEFT JOIN "Players" AS "b" ON "a"."id"="b"."player_id" GROUP BY 1,2
